$ SQL Developer: Tools -> Preferences -> Code Editor -> Fonts

The menu *Tools -> Preferences -> Code Editor -> Fonts* allows to change the font and its size for the *Worksheet* and the *Query Result* pane.

The chosen values are persistend under the → development/Software/Oracle-SQL-Developer/directories/user-information[user information directory] in
→ development/Software/Oracle-SQL-Developer/directories/user-information/systemV_W_X_Y_Z/o_sqldeveloper/product-preferences_xml[`SystemV.W.X.Y.Z/o.sqldeveloper/product-preferences.xml`].
